import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react";

// material-ui
import {

  Checkbox,
  FormControlLabel,
  Grid,
  Stack,
  Typography,
  TextField,
  Tooltip,
  IconButton,
  Divider,
} from "@mui/material";
import HelpIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Help";

// third-party
import { useFormik } from "formik";
import * as yup from "yup";

const Carrierform = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Grid container spacing={3}>

          <TextField
            id="accountnumber"
            name="faccountnumber"
            label="Your Carrier Account Number *"
            fullWidth

            id="carrieraccountid"

            fullWidth

        <Grid item lg={6} md={6} xs={6} sm={6}>
          <TextField id="clave" name="clave" label="Your Password" fullWidth />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item lg={12} md={12} xs={12} sm={6}>
          <TextField
            id="fdaRegister"
            name="fdaRegister"
            label="FDA Register Number"
            fullWidth
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item lg={12} md={12} xs={12} sm={6}>
          <TextField
            id="fdaRegister"
            name="fdaRegister"
            label="FDA Register Number"
            fullWidth
          />
         
        </Grid>
        <Divider />

    </>
  );
};

export default Carrierform;
